{
  "text": "which indeed matches our calculation in the previous section. Additionally, we repeated the above calculation using Cartesian coordinates (instead of polar coordinates) for the replica manifold, and we found precisely the same result stated above. [CITATION_1] In a way, this calculation makes transparent the fact that the cancellation of the anomalous entanglement response of the bulk and the domain wall CFT is forced upon us by the diffeomorphism invariance of the full theory on replica manifolds.",
